  <brief_title>Treosulfan-based Conditioning for Allogeneic Stem-cell Transplantation (SCT) in Lymphoid Malignancies</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of Fludarabine Combined With Intravenous Treosulfan and Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem-cell Transplantation in Patients With Lymphatic Malignancies</official_title>
